<h2 class="bold font-l">Kanna attacks Kobayashi</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Since she's in human form and low on mana, Kanna's strength and stamina are limited to that of an ordinary eight year old girl. As a result, her attempts to kill Kobayashi come off as more adorable than threatening. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WimpFight" class='trope-example-link'>Wimp Fight</a></p>
</div>
